app.c/h:
* Added: Interns interns to App.
* Calls InternInit, and InternFree.

intern.c/h:
* Implemented open-addressing linear probe intern table.
* Grows at 50% load.
* Stores its data in an AOB.
* Reinserts entries on growth to realign indices.
* Implements HashTag, preventing comparison against differing tags.
* Does its best to delay memcmp( ) until necessary.
* This table does not return a table index to the user of the API.
	It is an AOB offset. This is plenty enough for the parser to
	eventually distinguish if two strings are identical. If we need
	more metadata like exact lengths, we'll do it when the time comes.

log.c/h:
* Renamed: LogList to Logs.
* Renamed: LogList.bytes to Logs.aob

src.c/h:
* Renamed: SourceList to Srcs.
* Renamed: SourceList.bytes to Srcs.aob

lexer.c/h:
* Added: Interns pointer to lexer.
* LexId: Builds an Id hash, calls InternPutId, and stores the result on
	the token.